	<content><![CDATA[

Fragmentation is a breaking a packet into smaller pieces (fragment). 
Fragmentation is required when the datagram is larger than the MTU. 
Each fragment then becomes a datagram and transmitted independently from source. These datagrams are 
reassembled by the destination.


]]></content>
	<!-- Optional: Set a tabTrigger to define how to trigger the snippet -->
	<tabTrigger>fragmentation</tabTrigger>
</snippet>
